title: Fallen tree blocks road as motorists warned to take care
text:
• More details on our live traffic and travel service >> Share article 
The large tree has fallen on Misslebrook Lane, at the junction with the A27 Botley Road – the main road between Chilworth and North Baddesley . 
Motorists are being urged to take care as they approach the area. Promoted Stories Fallen tree causing delays on A27 between Chilworth and North Baddesley   Keep in touch with local news
